                Mr. Churchill
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-9861af30-f381-476b-8bc8-36e2429c1834" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
