    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Do I gather that the right hon. Gentleman says that the design of the most improved modern equipment was effected only towards the end of 1937?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-9861af30-f381-476b-8bc8-36e2429c1834" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1938-11-03/debates/37239a90-38f5-49fc-af52-e0058a2eeabb/Air-RaidDefence#contribution-9861af30-f381-476b-8bc8-36e2429c1834">
