        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-eb56749d-4faf-4c4f-89ea-963a03ea52fd">
                Mr. Hore-Belisha
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-eb56749d-4faf-4c4f-89ea-963a03ea52fd" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1938-11-03/debates/37239a90-38f5-49fc-af52-e0058a2eeabb/Air-RaidDefence#contribution-eb56749d-4faf-4c4f-89ea-963a03ea52fd">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">I did say so, and I have no doubt that some other instruments of defence will be designed in the next year. Defence is not a static, but a dynamic thing, and there is no means by which you can order a particular designer to produce a gun on a particular date. No Government can force the design of a gun before it is ready.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-eb56749d-4faf-4c4f-89ea-963a03ea52fd" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1938-11-03/debates/37239a90-38f5-49fc-af52-e0058a2eeabb/Air-RaidDefence#contribution-eb56749d-4faf-4c4f-89ea-963a03ea52fd">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
